# Ontology Storage

Per ADR-011:

- Ontology defined in version-controlled YAML under `packages/ontology/definitions/`
- Projected at runtime — not edited directly in the database
- Ontology Curator Agent creates `OntologyProposal` records — it cannot alter normative YAML directly
- Changes require approval workflow

## YAML structure

Each definition file includes `version`, `name`, `entity_types`, `relationship_types` with stable IDs.
